LayerD - Class in layers.double_based
This abstract class heavily outlines the functionality of a layer in a NeuralNetwork, using double as its basic calculation unit.

Constructs a LayerD with nbrNeurons neurons and nbrLinks links (the next layer in the network has nbrLinks neurons).
